Golf

Class Member

  • java.lang.Object
    • Golf.Member
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Golfer

    public class Member
extends java.lang.Object
    Member.java Member class is a parent of Golfer class for creating members of the golf club. Some members may not be golfers so this class creates member objects that have first name last name, email, and phone number. 
      Project: Golf Database
  Platform: jdk 1.7.0_17; NetBeans IDE 7.3; Windows 7
  Coarse: CS 142 Java II
  Hours: 2 hours
  Created on May 15, 2013
